# 🎮 BD Casual Gaming Platform Backend

A high-performance, real-time casual gaming and entertainment platform backend architecture tailored for high-concurrency environments. This platform focuses entirely on free-to-play skill games, engagement rewards, and secure point-based leaderboards.

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- **Runtime:** Node.js with TypeScript
- **Framework:** Express.js
- **Database ORM:** Prisma with PostgreSQL (Atomic transactions)
- **Caching & Real-time State:** Redis (Sorted Sets for leaderboards)
- **Communication Layer:** Socket.io (WebSockets)

## 🛠️ Features Implemented

- **Atomic Wallet System:** Isolated transactions to manage virtual points safely without race conditions.
- **Real-Time State Machine:** Scalable WebSocket integration via Socket.io for immediate win/loss broadcasts.
- **Optimized for Mobile:** Database schemas indexed tightly for quick mobile phone and OTP lookups.
- **CSPRNG Verification:** Cryptographically secure pseudo-random number generator structure logic.

